{"tid":603243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國竊取智慧財產問題 美國正式向WTO投訴","createTime":"2018-03-23T14:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T05:01:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9118431786b42ff17981f15cfd7ad20ee3439b","tid":603243,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpDGQvmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpDGQvmi.jpg&h=a6340557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國今日針對中國智慧財產（IP）問題，向世界貿易組織（WTO）正式投訴，是本週四美國總統川普宣布將對中國採取的貿易措施的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，美國今日發表聲明指出，「中國拒絕承認包括美國公司在內的海外版權持有者，已經破壞了WTO規定」，並且對海外科技強加不合理的合約條款，歧視進口技術，中國企業在技術授權結束後，仍不停止相關技術的使用。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國駐WTO大使則於昨日告訴媒體，中國已對美國的行動做好準備，中國當局今日也表示，他們正在採取抵抗措施，威脅將會對價值約30億美元（約新台幣874億元）的美國進口商品徵收關稅。<br />\n<br />\n這次川普向WTO投訴，是美國昨日宣布將對中國總值約600億美元（約新台幣1.7兆元）的進口商品徵收關稅後的後續行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2374838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2374838&d=9qwVmVD3aCsyYotQX9g%2BG5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7038948b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2374838&h=2e516f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2374838</a>"},{"pid":"b9bcc9b644d78db12aeb6c66ed3e232f659750fc","tid":603243,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"今日新聞先話中國將會投訴，呢頭美國轉數發發聲已經行前幾步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5744fe7517e49ea30cc2153d74f9ca49ffb6dca9","tid":603243,"uid":51183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"Make America Great Again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid